module.exports = {"data":{"post":{"id":"/home/travis/build/simonagren/simonagren.github.io/content/posts/2018-11-08--create-team-site-script/index.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark","html":"<p>I was asked a few days ago if we could automate <code class=\"language-text\">Microsoft Teams</code> creation when a Modern Team Site is created in SharePoint Online. I got to think about it and came up with one way at least. This is using an <code class=\"language-text\">Graph Beta endpoint</code> for the Team creation, so it’s not advisable to use this in production scenarios before it’s in <code class=\"language-text\">v1.0</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>We are going to create a Site Script that calls a Flow</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The Flow utilizes the Office365 Group(Unified) after the site is created and creates a Team via the Graph.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Since we are calling the Graph via Flow I’m setting up App Only permissions in the Azure AD for the application. </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Via PnP PowerShell we will:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Register the Hub Site</li>\n<li>Upload the Site Script and register withing Site Designs</li>\n<li>Create a Communication Site and make it a Hub Site</li>\n<li>Create a new Team Site and associate it to the Hub</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Setup App Permissions in Azure</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Open a new Notepad </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Go to the Azure Portal -> select Azure AD -> properties.\nCopy the <code class=\"language-text\">Directory ID</code> to Notepad\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/appid-7b01a536371e72e5a59010a71c7a73f2-9e89d.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 40.569395017793596%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"appid\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/appid-7b01a536371e72e5a59010a71c7a73f2-78f2b.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/appid-7b01a536371e72e5a59010a71c7a73f2-dce19.jpg 200w,\n/static/appid-7b01a536371e72e5a59010a71c7a73f2-c1413.jpg 400w,\n/static/appid-7b01a536371e72e5a59010a71c7a73f2-78f2b.jpg 800w,\n/static/appid-7b01a536371e72e5a59010a71c7a73f2-9e89d.jpg 843w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Select App Registrations -> Create new App and name it whatever you want -> then copy the <code class=\"language-text\">Application ID</code> to Notepad\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/appreg-092ffc7cfa45af8f794eca3b9627e38d-2183c.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 721px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 55.20110957004161%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"appreg\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/appreg-092ffc7cfa45af8f794eca3b9627e38d-2183c.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/appreg-092ffc7cfa45af8f794eca3b9627e38d-aab2e.jpg 200w,\n/static/appreg-092ffc7cfa45af8f794eca3b9627e38d-31a15.jpg 400w,\n/static/appreg-092ffc7cfa45af8f794eca3b9627e38d-2183c.jpg 721w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 721px) 100vw, 721px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Go to Settings -> Keys.\nCreate a new Key and Save to get the value. Copy the <code class=\"language-text\">Value</code> to Notepad\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/key-67201d6b9cedff8ff3ed3c46f57ad769-d4c43.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 34.39550140581068%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"key\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/key-67201d6b9cedff8ff3ed3c46f57ad769-78f2b.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/key-67201d6b9cedff8ff3ed3c46f57ad769-dce19.jpg 200w,\n/static/key-67201d6b9cedff8ff3ed3c46f57ad769-c1413.jpg 400w,\n/static/key-67201d6b9cedff8ff3ed3c46f57ad769-78f2b.jpg 800w,\n/static/key-67201d6b9cedff8ff3ed3c46f57ad769-d4c43.jpg 1067w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Go to Required Permissions -> Add Permission -> Select API -> Microsoft Graph -> under Application Permissions - Select <code class=\"language-text\">Read And Write All Groups</code>\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/permissions-c2296145f1939413df167d238fc327f3-27152.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 46.48148148148149%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"permissions\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/permissions-c2296145f1939413df167d238fc327f3-78f2b.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/permissions-c2296145f1939413df167d238fc327f3-dce19.jpg 200w,\n/static/permissions-c2296145f1939413df167d238fc327f3-c1413.jpg 400w,\n/static/permissions-c2296145f1939413df167d238fc327f3-78f2b.jpg 800w,\n/static/permissions-c2296145f1939413df167d238fc327f3-27152.jpg 1080w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Grant permissions\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/grant-466411b2ce248c2bc6495d39c73123c4-26122.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 744px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 35.34946236559139%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"grant\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/grant-466411b2ce248c2bc6495d39c73123c4-26122.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/grant-466411b2ce248c2bc6495d39c73123c4-11c12.jpg 200w,\n/static/grant-466411b2ce248c2bc6495d39c73123c4-453ee.jpg 400w,\n/static/grant-466411b2ce248c2bc6495d39c73123c4-26122.jpg 744w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 744px) 100vw, 744px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Create Flow</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Go to the Microsoft Flow site -> select Create from Blank</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Search for Request and select Request - When A HTTP Request is received\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/http-b3585e1e5b1cdd86bc853b0c949b0c1a-6c150.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 792px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 55.17676767676768%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"http\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/http-b3585e1e5b1cdd86bc853b0c949b0c1a-6c150.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/http-b3585e1e5b1cdd86bc853b0c949b0c1a-c1b29.jpg 200w,\n/static/http-b3585e1e5b1cdd86bc853b0c949b0c1a-ce23b.jpg 400w,\n/static/http-b3585e1e5b1cdd86bc853b0c949b0c1a-6c150.jpg 792w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 792px) 100vw, 792px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Copy the HTTP POST URL to Notepad -> then enter this JSON in the request body</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"object\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"properties\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"webUrl\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"webDescription\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"webTitle\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"creatorName\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"creatorEmail\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"createdTimeUTC\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"parameters\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"object\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"properties\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create new action - Search for Initialize and select Initialize Variable. Create three of these, rename them and enter the values from Notepad.\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/variables-c0e0871c53fe8144c2021ef7c26a0a83-3e4dc.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 777px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 96.01029601029602%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"variables\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/variables-c0e0871c53fe8144c2021ef7c26a0a83-3e4dc.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/variables-c0e0871c53fe8144c2021ef7c26a0a83-0d8a7.jpg 200w,\n/static/variables-c0e0871c53fe8144c2021ef7c26a0a83-1843c.jpg 400w,\n/static/variables-c0e0871c53fe8144c2021ef7c26a0a83-3e4dc.jpg 777w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 777px) 100vw, 777px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create new action - Search and select HTTP. Rename it and enter the values:</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><em>Method</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">POST</code></p>\n<p><em>Uri</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">https://login.windows.net/@{variables(&#39;TenantID&#39;)}/oauth2/token</code></p>\n<p><em>Headers</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">content-type: application/json;odata=verbose</code>\n<br>\n<em>Body</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">client_id=@{variables(&#39;ClientID&#39;)}&amp;client_Secret=@{variables(&#39;SecretID&#39;)}&amp;resource=https://graph.microsoft.com&amp;grant_type=client_credentials</code>\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/httptoken-703ea33e07db7d2cf3cae63b8fa7a6e8-e84e7.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 761px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 57.16162943495401%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"httptoken\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/httptoken-703ea33e07db7d2cf3cae63b8fa7a6e8-e84e7.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/httptoken-703ea33e07db7d2cf3cae63b8fa7a6e8-02fd0.jpg 200w,\n/static/httptoken-703ea33e07db7d2cf3cae63b8fa7a6e8-2fe4f.jpg 400w,\n/static/httptoken-703ea33e07db7d2cf3cae63b8fa7a6e8-e84e7.jpg 761w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 761px) 100vw, 761px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>\n<p>Create a new action - Parse JSON. Select body as content and enter this in the body:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"object\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"properties\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"token_type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"expires_in\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"ext_expires_in\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"expires_on\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"not_before\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"resource\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"access_token\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/parsetoken-a9d21e8a509e8593a91a30b1795cab8a-2cfcb.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 760px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 54.868421052631575%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"parsetoken\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/parsetoken-a9d21e8a509e8593a91a30b1795cab8a-2cfcb.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/parsetoken-a9d21e8a509e8593a91a30b1795cab8a-ee2d2.jpg 200w,\n/static/parsetoken-a9d21e8a509e8593a91a30b1795cab8a-53b66.jpg 400w,\n/static/parsetoken-a9d21e8a509e8593a91a30b1795cab8a-2cfcb.jpg 760w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create another HTTP action. Here we filter the groups based on the current site that triggered the flow. Which should be the modern Team Site we created.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><em>Method</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">GET</code></p>\n<p><em>Uri</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">https://graph.microsoft.com/v1.0/groups?$filter=displayName%20eq%20&#39;@{triggerBody()?[&#39;webTitle&#39;]}&#39;</code></p>\n<p><em>Headers</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">Authorization: Bearer @{body(&#39;Parse_and_get_Access_Token&#39;)?[&#39;access_token&#39;]}</code></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>\n<p>Create another Parse JSON. Select body as content. And enter this body:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"object\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"properties\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"@@odata.context\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"value\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"array\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"items\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"object\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"properties\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"id\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                    <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"string\"</span>\n                <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"required\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"id\"</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create Action Apply to each, which loops through all the items. We should only have one group, but anyways. Then inside it create a new HTTP action.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><em>Method</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">PUT</code></p>\n<p><em>Uri</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">https://graph.microsoft.com/beta/groups/@{items(&#39;Apply_to_each&#39;)?[&#39;id&#39;]}/team</code></p>\n<p><em>Headers</em>: <code class=\"language-text\">Authorization: Bearer @{body(&#39;Parse_and_get_Access_Token&#39;)?[&#39;access_token&#39;]}</code></p>\n<p><em>Body</em>: </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"memberSettings\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"allowCreateUpdateChannels\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"messagingSettings\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"allowUserEditMessages\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"allowUserDeleteMessages\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"funSettings\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"allowGiphy\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"giphyContentRating\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"strict\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/createteam-5c22edf11239db875dec153aae1931f9-0b939.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 794px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 103.27455919395467%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"createteam\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/createteam-5c22edf11239db875dec153aae1931f9-0b939.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/createteam-5c22edf11239db875dec153aae1931f9-0185e.jpg 200w,\n/static/createteam-5c22edf11239db875dec153aae1931f9-36ebe.jpg 400w,\n/static/createteam-5c22edf11239db875dec153aae1931f9-0b939.jpg 794w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h2>Create Site Script</h2>\n<p>So one of the actions in Site Scripts is <code class=\"language-text\">triggerFlow</code>. Since we are associating this Site Script to a Hub Site it will be run everytime a site is associated to the hub, for that site. The Flow will start and create the Team</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a .json file in Visual Studio Code. Use the following json and paste the HTTPPostUrl that we copied in to Notepad from the Flow</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\">\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"actions\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"verb\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"triggerFlow\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"url\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://prod-31.westeurope.logic.azure.com...\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Create Team\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    \n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2>Login and Create Site Design</h2>\n<p>As I stated earlier we’re going to use PnP PowerShell Commands to the extent it’s possible. They are doing an awesome job updating these, so it won’t be long until we can do all of this with PnP.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Connect to Tenant as Admin </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\">\n      <pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token variable\">$admin</span>=<span class=\"token string\">\"user.name@tenant.onmicrosoft.com\"</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$cred</span> = Get<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Credential <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>UserName <span class=\"token variable\">$admin</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Message <span class=\"token string\">\"Admin\"</span>\nConnect<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>PnPOnline <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Url https:<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>tenant<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>admin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sharepoint<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Credential <span class=\"token variable\">$cred</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Upload and add Site Script and Site Design</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\">\n      <pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token variable\">$scriptFromFile</span> = <span class=\"token function\">Get-Content</span> <span class=\"token string\">'C:\\Users\\...createTeam.json'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Raw\n<span class=\"token variable\">$siteScript</span> = Add<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>PnPSiteScript <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Title <span class=\"token string\">\"Auto Create Team\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Description <span class=\"token string\">\"Creates Team based on teamsite\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Content <span class=\"token variable\">$siteScript</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$siteDesign</span> = Add<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>PnPSiteDesign <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Title <span class=\"token string\">\"Auto Create Team\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>WebTemplate <span class=\"token string\">\"64\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>SiteScriptIds <span class=\"token variable\">$mySiteScript</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Id <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Description <span class=\"token string\">\"Creates Team base on teamsite\"</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Create Communication site and set as hub site</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create CommunicationSite</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\">\n      <pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token variable\">$hub</span> =  New<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>PnPSite <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token function\">Type</span> CommunicationSite <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Title <span class=\"token string\">\"Project Hub\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Url <span class=\"token string\">\"https://tenant.sharepoint.com/sites/projecthub\"</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Register as Hub Site</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\">\n      <pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\">Register<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>PnPHubSite <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Site <span class=\"token variable\">$hub</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Associate Site Design with Hub Site</h2>\n<p>Right now Set-PnPHubSite doesn’t seem to have the ability to set Site Design, so I’m using Set-SpOHubSite instead.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Connect again, but via SPO (Sorry for this)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\">\n      <pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token variable\">$admin</span>=<span class=\"token string\">\"user.name@tenant.onmicrosoft.com\"</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$cred</span> = Get<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Credential <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>UserName <span class=\"token variable\">$admin</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Message <span class=\"token string\">\"Admin\"</span>\nConnect<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>SpOService <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Url https:<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>tenant<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>admin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sharepoint<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Credential <span class=\"token variable\">$cred</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add default Site Design to Hub</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\">\n      <pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token function\">Set</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>SpOHubSite <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Identity <span class=\"token variable\">$hub</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ID <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>SiteDesignId <span class=\"token variable\">$siteDesign</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Id</code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Create Modern Team Site and associate to hubsite</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Create Team Site</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\">\n      <pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token variable\">$teamSite</span> = New<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>PnPSite <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token function\">Type</span> TeamSite <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Title <span class=\"token string\">\"Project 1\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Alias <span class=\"token string\">\"project1\"</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Associate to Hub Site</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\">\n      <pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\">Add<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>PnPHubSiteAssociation <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>Site <span class=\"token variable\">$teamSite</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>HubSite <span class=\"token string\">\"https://tenant.sharepoint.com/sites/projecthub\"</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Now let the Flow Do It’s Work</h2>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/success-b3efa29ae13967ac3136f9727b3cd824-f3f84.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.33865814696487%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"success\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/success-b3efa29ae13967ac3136f9727b3cd824-78f2b.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/success-b3efa29ae13967ac3136f9727b3cd824-dce19.jpg 200w,\n/static/success-b3efa29ae13967ac3136f9727b3cd824-c1413.jpg 400w,\n/static/success-b3efa29ae13967ac3136f9727b3cd824-78f2b.jpg 800w,\n/static/success-b3efa29ae13967ac3136f9727b3cd824-ab4c4.jpg 1200w,\n/static/success-b3efa29ae13967ac3136f9727b3cd824-f3f84.jpg 1252w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>","fields":{"slug":"/create-team-site-script/","prefix":"2018-11-08"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Create a Team using site scripts, Flow and Hub Sites","author":"Simon Ågren","category":null,"tags":["Flow","SharePoint Online","Site Scripts","Graph"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/success-b3efa29ae13967ac3136f9727b3cd824-ada8c.jpg"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"/home/travis/build/simonagren/simonagren.github.io/content/parts/author.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark","html":"<p><strong>Simon Ågren</strong> Passionate about SharePoint and Office365. Solution Architect working as a consultant for Sogeti in Umeå, Sweden.</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":"2263145610597628"}}}},"pathContext":{"slug":"/create-team-site-script/","prev":{"id":"/home/travis/build/simonagren/simonagren.github.io/content/posts/2018-11-07--hello-world/index.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark","fields":{"slug":"/hello-world/","prefix":"2018-11-07"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Hello World - a first blog post","category":null,"tags":["hello","gatsby","github"]}}}}


